    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>https://shichenliu.github.io/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://shichenliu.github.io/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Stealth mode. I was a senior research scientist at Google.&#xA;I obtained my Ph.D. from the University of Southern California, &lt;a href=&#34;https://vgl.ict.usc.edu&#34;&gt;VGL-ICT&lt;/a&gt;.&#xA;Previously, I was in the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/thuml&#34;&gt;Machine Learning Group&lt;/a&gt;, Tsinghua University, advised by &lt;a href=&#34;http://ise.thss.tsinghua.edu.cn/~mlong/&#34;&gt;Prof. Mingsheng Long&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;http://yue-cao.me/&#34;&gt;Dr. Yue Cao&lt;/a&gt;.&#xA;I visited the &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.cs.cornell.edu/~kilian/index.html&#34;&gt;Prof. Kilian Q. Weinberger&lt;/a&gt;&amp;rsquo;s lab at Cornell University, working with &lt;a href=&#34;https://gaohuang-net.github.io/&#34;&gt;Prof. Gao Huang&lt;/a&gt;.&#xA;My research explores principled methods for understanding the 3D world and creating advanced digital human technologies.&#xA;I&amp;rsquo;m also a photographer, digital artist, and gamer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
